title: "CaseLaw-Bench: A Graded-Relevance Benchmark for Chinese Civil/Commercial Similar-Case Retrieval (Phase 1: Sales Contracts, Shanghai)"
abstract: >-
  民商事类案检索的分级相关性标准答案集。Phase 1 = 买卖合同纠纷(上海),
  58 条自然语言问句 × 751 篇案件,LLM 双判官集成(deepseek-chat × deepseek-v4-pro)
  pointwise 标注,grade 0–3。基于最高法《指导意见》三要素 + 三步法。
type: dataset
